snippet.description:

Lyrics & Composition: Neha Kakkar

Saari saari raat mere super ch Aunda h
Eni cute laga roz Milan nu aunda h -2

Mere kol aake galla nu touch kare 
Mere kol aake galla nu touch kare
Kehnda tu hi chahidi mainu 

Main taan vyah krvauna tere naal h 
Zindagi da gujara tere naal h

Agli vaari avngaaa te mummy ji nu lavanga cute jahi bhu da introduction krvangaaa -2 
Kehnda sabr ni hunda honeymoon te jana
Das kithe leke chala meri doll nu

Main taan Viah  krvauna tere naal h 
Zindagi da gujara tere naal h

Kehnda shopping te chal fir dinner krnga kite baar ek ni do ni leke dena tainu leke dunga lehange hazaar

O jaan meri zara smile dikha teri smile eni lagdi kamal h 

Main taan vyah krvauna tere naal h 
Zindagi da gujara tere naal h -2

snippet.title: Ae Mere Dil (Video) Jeet Gannguli ft. Abhay Jodhpurkar | Manoj M | Shaheer Sheikh, Tejasswi Prakash
snippet.description:
VYRL Originals presents Jeet Gannguli’s Ae Mere Dil. A soulful ballad sung by the versatile Abhay Jodhpurkar and the lyrics have been penned by Manoj Muntashir. The music video stars Shaheer Sheikh & Tejasswi Prakash as they are seen taking you on an emotional journey. The song talks about how some events in life, can make it difficult for you to trust people, specially loved ones. 
Every broken heart gets a second chance, it is up to you to embrace it.

Watch till the end to see how the story unfolds, how would you deal with a situation like this, tell us in the comments below.

snippet.title: Ludo | Official Trailer | Abhishek A Bachchan, Aditya Roy Kapur, Rajkummar Rao, Pankaj Tripathi
snippet.description:
What happens when life is a literal roll of the dice?

Ludo is about the butterfly effect and how, despite all the chaos and crowd of the world, all our lives are inextricably connected. Starring an amazing ensemble cast of Abhishek A Bachchan, Aditya Roy Kapur, Rajkummar Rao, Pankaj Tripathi, Rohit Saraf, Fatima Sana Sheikh, Sanya Malhotra, Pearle Maaney,  Inayat Verma, Asha Negi and Shalini Vats, Ludo is four different stories tied together by unavoidable circumstances and coincidences far beyond our understanding, all of which make up for a crazy caper of a film.

Catch the madness, only on Netflix, on 12th November.

Directed by: Anurag Basu
Produced by: Bhushan Kumar, Divya Khosla Kumar, Krishan Kumar, T-Series Films, Anurag Basu, Tani Basu, Anurag Basu Productions
Music by: Pritam
Lyrics by: Sayeed Quadri, Sandeep Shrivastava & Swanand Kirkire
Music Partner: T-Series Music

snippet.title: Chhalaang: Care Ni Karda | Rajkummar R, Nushrratt B | Yo Yo Honey Singh, Alfaaz, Hommie Dilliwala
snippet.description:
Gulshan Kumar & T-Series Films present, official video song "Care Ni Karda" from bollywood movie  Chhalaang starring Rajkummar Rao & Nushrratt Bharuccha. The film is written by Luv Ranjan, Aseem Arrora & Zeishan Quadri, it is directed by Hansal Mehta, produced by Ajay Devgn, Luv Ranjan & Ankur Garg, and presented by Bhushan Kumar.  

Chhalaang is slated to release on Amazon Prime Video, this Diwali, Nov 13.

Chhalaang is a hilarious, yet inspirational journey of a PT Master from a semi government funded school in Northern India. Montu (Rajkummar Rao) is a typical PT Master for whom it’s just a job. When circumstances put everything that Montu cares for at stake, including Neelu (Nushrratt Bharuccha) who he loves, Montu is forced to do what he has never done - Teach. Through Montu’s journey, Chhalaang humorously addresses the value of Sports Education in the school curriculum.

snippet.title: Zee Tamil Kudumbam Viruthugal 2020 | 25th October 2020, Sunday 2:30 PM | Promo
snippet.description:

snippet.title: जो तेरी डोली उठी, ज़माने को जला दूंगा - Diljale [1996] - Movie Part 02 - Ajay Devgn | Sonali Bendre
snippet.description:
Subscribe to Shemaroo - http://bit.ly/2DNFnzF

Diljale is a story about love and patriotism. Captain Ranvir is assigned the task of apprehending two terrorists named Shaka and Dara. Upon arrival in the region, he falls in love with Radhika, the daughter of Rajasaheb, who also is a Minister. The latter approves of him, and arranges his wedding with his daughter. Before the engagement could take place, Ranvir finds out that he has a rival in Shaka, who was in love with Radhika before, and is all set to prevent this marriage at any and costs. Ranvir decides to postpone his wedding until such time he arrests Shaka and his associates - a decision that will not only pit him against well-armed terrorists, but also result in the abduction of a bus-load of Vaishnodevi devotees - which include Radhika and her Bua. Watch the film to know the backstory of Shaka and Radhika.

#Ajaydevgan #Diljale #bollywoodmovie

snippet.title: Raya and the Last Dragon | Official Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Restore peace. Find the last dragon. Watch the new trailer for Raya and the Last Dragon, in theaters March 2021.

Long ago, in the fantasy world of Kumandra, humans and dragons lived together in harmony. But when an evil force threatened the land, the dragons sacrificed themselves to save humanity. Now, 500 years later, that same evil has returned and it’s up to a lone warrior, Raya, to track down the legendary last dragon to restore the fractured land and its divided people. However, along her journey, she’ll learn that it’ll take more than a dragon to save the world—it’s going to take trust and teamwork as well. From directors Don Hall and Carlos López Estrada, co-directors Paul Briggs and John Ripa, producers Osnat Shurer and Peter Del Vecho, and featuring the voices of Kelly Marie Tran as Raya and Awkwafina as the last dragon Sisu, Walt Disney Animation Studios’ “Raya and the Last Dragon” opens in U.S. theaters on March 2021.

Facebook:  https://www.facebook.com/rayaandthelastdragon
Twitter:  https://twitter.com/DisneyRaya
Instagram:  https://www.instagram.com/disneyraya/
Hashtag: #DisneyRaya

snippet.title: Fortnitemares 2020 Midas' Revenge Gameplay Trailer - Fortnite
snippet.description:
Vengeance is a dish best... served... GOLD! Read more here: https://www.epicgames.com/fortnite/news/join-shadow-midas-to-get-revenge-in-fortnitemares-2020

Fortnitemares is back! From October 21 until November 3, rise to the occasion in the return of Fortnitemares. In Fortnitemares 2020: Midas’ Revenge, don’t let the tomb hold you back from haunting the living. And while you’re at it, live up your afterlife by vanquishing Challenges, catching a party, touring the Ghoulish Isles, and even cosplaying IRL.

Shadow Midas has taken over The Authority with his reawakened Henchmen. Stop him before you turn into a Shadow yourself. After being eliminated in Solo, Duos, or Squads, return to battle as a Shadow for your shot at a Shadow Royale. Join fellow Shadows to defeat survivors by using your otherworldly abilities, like possessing the body of vehicles…

Over the course of Fortnitemares, complete new Challenges to unlock special in-game rewards, including the Midas’ Shadow Wrap, Smash O’-Lantern Pickaxe, Bobo Back Bling, and more! Be seasonally-appropriate or stay scary year-round.

Also, Reggaeton Global ambassador superstar and four-time Latin GRAMMYⓇ winner J Balvin comes to Party Royale with the Afterlife Party, a special performance of Latin culture and hip-hop including the debut of his brand new song ft. Sech! The party begins at the Main Stage in Party Royale on October 31 at 9 PM ET (6 PM PT). 

Jump into Fortnitemares now!

#Fortnitemares #FortnitemaresChallenges #Fortnite


Play Fortnite Battle Royale, the completely free 100-player PvP mode. One giant map, A Battle Bus, Last one standing wins. ESRB Rating: Teen with Violence.

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/fortnite/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/FortniteGame
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/FortniteGame/

Learn More: https://www.epicgames.com/fortnite/en-US/

snippet.title: Paris Saint-Germain vs. Manchester United: Extended Highlights | UCL on CBS
snippet.description:
A Bruno Fernandes penalty chance got things started off in Paris as Manchester United buried its opportunity to take control 1-0 in the 23’. 
From there PSG kept creating chances until they tied it up in the 55’ off an Anthony Martial own goal off of a corner kick. Manchester United would eventually answer back late in the second half, burying it right where PSG keeper Keylor Navas couldn’t reach it, giving them a 2-1 lead in the 87’. 
Manchester United would hold on for the final minutes to secure a decisive win over PSG away from home. 

Stream every UEFA Champions League match live on CBS All Access:
http://bit.ly/ucloncbssports

snippet.title: Finding Out We're Pregnant | Sadie Robertson Huff and Christian Huff's Pregnancy Story!
snippet.description:
We're Pregnant! If you didn't already know -- we are expecting a baby! We wanted to share our pregnancy story on how we found out we are pregnant, and wanted to answer some questions about baby Huff. Watch the whole video to find out the step by step story of what was happening when we found out we're going to have a baby, how I revealed the baby news to Christian, and how we made the pregnancy announcement to our family and friends! - xo, Sadie

Get More Encouraging Videos by Subscribing: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCl2vodgsQPqVhbZNGNyjUiQ?sub_confirmation=1

Video Chapters:
- Were we trying? 00:29
- Were we surprised? 00:39
- Were we in quarantine? 00:43

- Sadie took a pregnancy test: 05:14

- Telling Christian's Mom and Dad they're pregnant: 10:30
- Who had the best reaction? 11:13

- Who will the baby look like? Leave a Comment: 12:57
- Video and Photo Montage: 14:10

Visit: https://liveoriginal.com
Follow: https://www.instagram.com/legitsadierob
Like: https://www.facebook.com/sadiecrobertson/
Tweet: https://twitter.com/sadierob
Join: http://eepurl.com/cYQOvf


ABOUT SADIE ROBERTSON:
Sadie Robertson, first introduced to the world as a star of A&E’s Duck Dynasty and ABC’s Dancing with the Stars, recognized she could be a positive voice to those in need of an inspiring presence in their lives. At the age of twenty-two, she’s become one of the most prominent voices of her generation. Sadie’s passion is to speak, to write, and to encourage. She is a sister and friend to more than five million followers on her various social platforms, which she sees as a direct line of communication to her peers.

Sadie’s creative and entrepreneurial spirit has helped her become a 'New York Times Best Selling Author', and launch her Live Original brand, which speaks to millions across her various platforms, including YouTube, social media, the Live Original blog, LO Fam Community, the Live Original tour, and her Whoa That’s Good podcast.

Additionally, Robertson has long poured her heart into philanthropic efforts. She has loved partnering with Roma Boots, Help One Now, World Vision, and the World Food Program over the last few years. To date, Robertson has been able to be a voice and agent of change in many countries, including Peru, Somalia, Moldova, and the Dominican Republic.

Sadie is newly married to the man of her dreams, Christian Huff, and is looking forward to continuing to learn what it means to truly live and celebrate in every moment of life.

snippet.title: Real Madrid vs. Shakhtar Donetsk: Extended Highlights | UCL on CBS Sports
snippet.description:
Shakhtar came into Matchday 1 severely outmanned as they were down 10 men due to COVID. Despite being down players they created opportunities and gave Zinedine Zidane and his Real Madrid squad problems from start to finish.  
Shakhtar came out with a strong offensive plan and put the pressure on Real Madrid early and often. The early offensive pressure resulted in a goal in the 29’ by Tetê thrusting the Ukranian side to an early 1-0 lead. 
Not long after the goal, Tetê was causing problems again. He took a shot from the top of the box causing Real Madrid’s keeper, Thibaut Courtois, to deflect the ball back into play, but it went off of his own defender, Raphaël Varane, for an own goal giving Shakhtar a commanding 2-0 lead in the 33’. 
Tetê wasn’t done leaving his mark on the first half though, in the 42’ he played a beautiful back heel pass to an open Manor Solomon who drilled it to the bottom left corner of the goal to bolster Shakhtar’s lead over Real Madrid, 3-0. 
Real Madrid started the second half playing with more fire, and they got things going with an absolute banger of a goal in the 54’ by Luka Modrić from 30 meters. Real Madrid kept the pressure on by scoring its second goal just 5 minutes later in the 59’ by Vinícius Júnior who had just come on to the pitch after being on the bench for the first half. Real Madrid had one final opportunity late in the second half to pull even, but Vinícius Júnior was ruled offside via VAR and the goal was called off. 

Stream every UEFA Champions League match live on CBS All Access:
http://bit.ly/ucloncbssports

snippet.title: Watch Three Space Travelers Return Home from the International Space Station
snippet.description:
NASA astronaut Chris Cassidy and cosmonauts Anatoly Ivanishin and Ivan Vagner of Roscosmos will return to Earth from the International Space Station on Wed., Oct. 21, 2020. Tune in for deorbit burn and landing coverage as their Soyuz spacecraft descends to a parachute-assisted landing, set for 10:55 p.m. EDT southeast of the remote town of Dzhezkazgan, Kazakhstan. 




The three crew members will wrap up a 196-day mission spanning 3,136 orbits of Earth and 83 million miles. Cassidy is completing his third spaceflight for a total of 378 days in space, the fifth highest total among U.S. astronauts. Ivanishin is completing his third flight into space, totaling 476 days. This was Vagner’s first spaceflight. During their expedition, Cassidy, Ivanishin, and Vagner welcomed the arrival of NASA astronauts Robert Behnken and Douglas Hurley on NASA’s SpaceX Demo-2 mission, the first crewed flight of a commercial spacecraft and the first launch of humans from American soil to the space station since 2011.

snippet.title: Epic Road Trip, a Blown Up Hemi, and Goodbye 6 Door Ford! Finnegan's Garage Ep.117
snippet.description:
This trip was so good that we had to split the video into two parts because so much stuff happened. First off, here's a little life update; We filmed this back in September but didn't get time to edit and upload the video until now. Immediately after filming our trip to Rocky Mountain Raceweek 2.0 (which is not in the Rocky Mountains), we left town to film Roadkill and Faster With Finnegan and we still aren't done filming those shows so we are working on Finnegan's Garage edits in our spare time. 
Anyway, since September, a lot has happened. I've bought a new enclosed ramp truck, which you'll briefly see in this video, I've traded away the six-door Ford F650 for a '66 Chevy Suburban, which you'll also see in this video, too. We also had a small shift linkage issue in Blasphemi during Rocky Mountain Raceweek 2.0, which resulted in a major engine failure-again, it's in this video. 
With any luck we'll upload Part 2 of the video next week. In that video, you'll see the rest of the road trip and you get to see my wife cry when I surprise her on our 15th wedding anniversary. :)

03:37 If you'd like to grab the cool LED lights from WireCare.com we used on our trailer in this episode then go here: 

https://www.wirecare.com/interest/audio-visual/led/led-lighting-kits/as-rgb5mk2-5m-kit-rgb-5050-led-strip-44ky

Check out Rugged Radios which we would have used way more if not for the small engine failure!:
https://www.ruggedradios.com

If you'd like your own Finnegan Speed and Marine shirt, hats or stickers then go here: 
www.fsmgarage.com
All proceeds will go toward fixing the damn Hemi-again! lol

thanks!

-Finnegan

snippet.title: Barcelona vs. Ferencváros: Extended Highlights | UCL on CBS
snippet.description:
Messi started the game doing things only Messi can do, dribbling into the box and forcing a bad challenge by Ferencváros which created a penalty chance. Messi buried the penalty in the bottom right corner giving Barcelona a 1-0 lead in the 27’. 
Later in the first half, Frenkie de Jong played a perfect ball into the box to 17-year-old phenom Ansu Fati who sliced it right into the back of the net giving Barcelona a 2-0 lead.
Ferencváros would make things a little tighter in the second half with a penalty goal in the 71’ after Gerard Piqué was issued a red card for interfering with a goal opportunity. 
Barcelona would keep pouring it on in the second half with goals by Philippe Coutinho, Pedri and Ousmane Dembélé. 
Barcelona wouldn’t look back and go on to win the match, 5-1.

Stream every UEFA Champions League match live on CBS All Access:
http://bit.ly/ucloncbssports

#UCL #Barcelona #Ferencváros #LionelMessi #Messi #deJong #AnsuFati #penaltykick #goal #redcard #pique

snippet.title: Apex Legends Fight or Fright Event 2020 Trailer
snippet.description:
Trick-or-treat yourself to the Fight or Fright Event, October 22 - November 3! Scary new mode, spooky challenges, and spectacular rewards. Learn More

Play the new “Shadow Royale” LTM on Kings Canyon After Dark, where death is just the start. Respawn as a Shadow to haunt your enemies and help your squad. With freakish speed, deadly claws, and the ability to revive your teammates, you won’t miss a step. And you can keep going until your whole squad is wiped out. Plus complete frightening challenges to earn freaky free rewards and outfit your Legends with new and classic Halloween cosmetics in the store. Ready to terrorize the Arena?

Apex Legends™ is a free-to-play battle royale game where legendary characters battle for glory, fame, and fortune on the fringes of the Frontier. Play for free now on Xbox One, PS4, and Origin for PC. 

Learn more about Apex Legends Season 6 – Boosted: http://x.ea.com/64060
 
Check out our YouTube channel: http://x.ea.com/56710.

localizations.ja.title: エーペックスレジェンズ ファイト・オア・フライト イベント トレーラー
localizations.ja.description:
トリック・オア・トリート！10月22日～11月3日までファイト・オア・フライト イベントを開催！恐怖の最新モードや戦慄のチャレンジ、鳥肌ものの報酬が君を待っている。詳細をチェック

闇夜のキングスキャニオンを舞台に、新期間限定モードの「シャドウロワイヤル」が登場。ここでは死すら始まりに過ぎない。倒されても影としてリスポーンし、敵を倒して味方を助けることができる。高速移動が可能な影は攻撃力にも優れており、仲間を復活させるアビリティまで備えている。どんな相手にも太刀打ちできる存在だ。そして、戦いは仲間がすべて消されるまで続く。加えて、戦慄のチャレンジをクリアすれば、鳥肌ものの報酬が無料でゲット可能。好きなレジェンドのハロウィン仕様の新旧装飾アイテムもストアに登場する。戦場を恐怖に染めよ！

「エーペックスレジェンズ™」は、伝説の戦士が集結してフロンティアの辺境で富と栄誉と名声を懸けて戦う、基本プレイ無料のバトルロイヤル作品。Xbox One、PS4、Origin（PC）で今すぐ無料プレイ。

localizations.es-ES.description:
¡Atrévete a sumergirte en el evento Lucha o pesadilla, desde el 22 de octubre al 3 de noviembre! Un siniestro modo nuevo, retos espeluznantes y recompensas espectaculares. Más información

Juega al nuevo modo por tiempo limitado Shadow Royale en Cañón de los Reyes de noche: aquí, la muerte es solo el principio. Reaparece en forma de sombra para perseguir a los enemigos y ayudar a tu pelotón. Con una velocidad increíble, unas garras letales y la capacidad de reanimar a tus compañeros, tendrás la victoria al alcance de la mano. Y podrás continuar hasta que aniquilen a todo el pelotón. Además, completa retos aterradores para conseguir recompensas gratuitas y viste a tus leyendas con los elementos cosméticos de Halloween nuevos y clásicos que encontrarás en la tienda. ¿Listo para aterrorizar a la arena?

Apex Legends™ es un juego de Battle Royale gratuito donde personajes legendarios se enfrentan para lograr gloria, fama y fortuna en los confines de la Frontera. Juega ya gratis en Xbox One, PS4 y Origin para PC.

localizations.pt-BR.description:
Procure doçuras ou travessuras com o Evento Luta ou Fuga, de 22 de outubro a 3 de novembro! Novo modo assustador, desafios assombrosos e recompensas espetaculares. Saiba mais

Jogue o novo modo por tempo limitado ""Sombra Royale"" no Desfiladeiro do Rei (Noite), onde a morte é só o começo. Renasça como uma Sombra para assombrar seus inimigos e ajudar seu esquadrão. Com velocidade alucinante, garras mortais e a habilidade de reviver os aliados, é uma ótima pós-vida. E você continua na partida até todo o seu esquadrão ser eliminado. Além disso, conclua desafios assombrosos para ganhar recompensas e trajes únicos para suas Lendas, junto aos novos e clássicos itens cosméticos de Halloween na loja. Tudo pronto para aterrorizar a Arena?

Velocidade estonteante, garras mortíferas e a habilidade de reanimar os teus companheiros de equipa vão tornar-te imparável. E, enquanto o teu esquadrão não for eliminado, não tens de parar. localizations.ko.title: Apex 레전드 – 싸우거나 도망가거나 수집품 이벤트 트레일러
localizations.ko.description:
10월 22일 - 11월 3일 진행되는 싸우거나 도망가거나 이벤트에서 할로윈 분위기를 느껴보십시오! 무서운 신규 모드, 으스스한 챌린지, 엄청난 보상을 획득하십시오. 자세히 보기

밤의 킹스 캐년에서 펼쳐지는 신규 기간 한정 모드 ""섀도우 로얄""을 플레이하십시오. 죽음은 시작일 뿐입니다. 그림자로 부활하여 적에게 공포를 선사하고 아군 분대를 도우십시오. 괴물 같은 속도와 치명적인 손톱, 아군을 회생시킬 수 있는 능력으로 끝까지 게임에 참여할 수 있습니다. 그림자는 분대 전멸 이전까지 계속해서 싸우게 됩니다. 무서운 챌린지를 완수하여 기괴한 무료 보상을 획득하고 스토어에서 새로운 클래식 할로윈 치장 아이템으로 레전드를 꾸미십시오. 아레나에 공포를 불러올 준비 되셨습니까?

Apex 레전드™는 전설적인 캐릭터들이 영광과 명성, 부를 쟁취하기 위해 프런티어의 변경에서 치열한 전투를 벌이는 부분 유료 배틀 로얄 게임입니다. Xbox One, PlayStation 4 및 PC용 Origin에서 Apex 레전드를 무료 플레이하십시오.

localizations.no.description:
Knask eller knep deg gjennom «Fight or Fright»-hendelsen, fra 22. oktober til 3. november! Skummel ny modus, skumle utfordringer og spektakulære belønninger. Les mer

Spill den tidsbegrensede «Shadow Royale»-modusen på Kings Canyon After Dark, hvor døden bare er begynnelsen. Kom tilbake som en skygge for å hjemsøke fiendene dine og hjelp laget ditt. Et skremmende tempo, dødsfarlige klør og en evne til å gjenopplive lagkamerater vil holde deg aktiv. Og du kan fortsette helt frem til hele laget ditt blir utslettet. Pluss at du kan fullføre skremmende utfordringer for å få gysende gratisbelønninger og kle legendene dine med nye og klassiske Halloween-elementer fra butikken. Klar til å terrorisere arenaen?

Apex Legends™ er et gratis battle royale-spill hvor legendariske karakterer kjemper om rikdom og ære i utkanten av grenselandet. Spill gratis på Xbox One, PS4 og Origin for PC nå.

localizations.fr-FR.description:
Faites le plein de frissons pendant l'événement Combat ou Effroi, du 22 octobre au 3 novembre ! Découvrez un nouveau mode effrayant, relevez des défis terrifiants et décrochez des récompenses spectaculaires. En savoir plus

Jouez au mode Fantôme Royale à durée limitée dans la version nocturne du Canyon des Rois, où la mort n'est qu'un début. Réapparaissez en tant que fantôme pour hanter vos ennemis et aider votre escouade. Vitesse ahurissante, griffes acérées et capacités avancées de réanimation : vous serez au centre de l'attention ! La partie ne prend fin que lorsque la dernière Légende rend l'âme. Relevez également de sinistres défis pour décrocher des récompenses horrifiques, et obtenez des tenues et des objets cosmétiques pour vos Légendes sur le thème d'Halloween dans la Boutique. Qui va terroriser l'arène ?

Apex Legends™ est un jeu de tir Battle Royale Free-to-Play où des personnages légendaires combattent ensemble aux confins de la Frontière pour la gloire et la fortune. Jouez gratuitement sur PlayStation 4, Xbox One et Origin pour PC.

Och du kan fortsätta tills hela din grupp är utplånad. Plus kompletta skrämmande utmaningar för att tjäna galna gratisbelöningar och klä dina legendarer med ny och klassisk Halloween-kosmetika i butiken. Redo att terrorisera arenan?

localizations.it.title: Apex Legends - Evento Paura del buio - Il trailer
localizations.it.description:
Dolcetto o scherzetto? L'evento Paura del buio ti aspetta dal 22 ottobre al 3 novembre! Una modalità spettrale, nuove sfide inquietanti e ricompense da paura. Scopri di più

Gioca la nuova modalità a tempo limitato Shadow Royale nel Canyon dei Re notturno, dove la morte non è che l'inizio. Rientra in gioco come ombra per trasformarti nel peggiore incubo dei nemici e aiutare la tua squadra. Con una velocità a dir poco mostruosa, artigli letali e la possibilità di rianimare i tuoi compagni, batterti sarà difficile. E continuerai a tornare finché l'intera squadra non sarà eliminata! Infine, completa sfide spaventose per ottenere stravaganti ricompense gratuite e dai un'occhiata al negozio per rifare il look alle tue leggende con oggetti cosmetici di Halloween vecchi e nuovi. Semina il terrore nell'arena!

Apex Legends™ è un gioco gratuito in stile battle royale in cui personaggi leggendari si sfidano per gloria, fama e ricchezza ai margini della Frontiera. Gioca gratis su Xbox One, PlayStation 4 e Origin per PC.

Speel de nieuwe ""Shadow Royale” LTM in Kings Canyon After Dark, waar de dood pas het begin is. Respawn als Shadow om de vijand te achtervolgen en je squad te helpen. Met bizarre snelheid, dodelijke klauwen en de mogelijkheid om teamleden tot leven te wekken, is elke klap raak. En je kunt doorgaan totdat het hele squad is weggevaagd. Overwin daarnaast angstaanjagende uitdagingen om bizarre gratis beloningen te verdienen en je Legends uit te rusten met nieuwe en klassieke cosmetische Halloween-items in de store. Ben je klaar om de Arena te terroriseren?

localizations.ru.title: Apex Legends — трейлер события «Бейся или бойся»
localizations.ru.description:
Побалуйте себя событием «Бейся или бойся», которое пройдет с 22 октября по 3 ноября! Жуткий новый режим, страшные испытания и превосходные награды. Подробнее

Сыграйте в новом временном режиме «Королевская битва теней» в ночном Каньоне Кингс, где смерть — это только начало. Возрождайтесь в виде тени и вредите врагам, а также помогайте отряду. Чудовищная скорость, острые когти и способность реанимировать союзников не дадут вам соскучиться. Более того, вы сможете сражаться, пока враги не перебьют весь ваш отряд. Но это еще не все: проходите страшные испытания, чтобы заработать жуткие бесплатные награды и облики для легенд, а также не упустите возможность закупить новые и классические хэллоуинские предметы внешнего вида в магазине. Готовы терроризировать арену?

Apex Legends™ — бесплатная игра в жанре «королевская битва», где легендарные персонажи сражаются за славу и богатства на дальних рубежах Фронтира. Играйте бесплатно на Xbox One, PS4 и в Origin для ПК.

Keppostele sydämesi kyllyydestä Fight or Fright -tapahtumassa 22. lokakuuta – 3. marraskuuta! Luvassa uusi pelottava pelitila, hirmuisia haasteita ja mahtavia palkintoja. Lue lisää

Pelaa uutta rajoitetun ajan Shadow Royale -pelitilaa Kings Canyon After Darkissa – kuolema on vasta alkua. Palaa peliin varjona vaanimaan vihollisiasi ja auttamaan tiimiäsi. Hyödynnä epätavallinen nopeus, tappavat kynnet ja kyky elvyttää tiimiläisiäsi. Voit jatkaa pelaamista varjona, kunnes koko tiimisi on mennyttä. Ansaitse myös selkäpiitä karmivia maksuttomia palkintoja suorittamalla hirmuisia haasteita ja varusta Legendasi kaupassa uusiin sekä klassisiin halloweenasuihin. Oletko valmis herättämään kauhua areenalla?

Apex Legends™ on ilmainen battle royale -peli, jossa legendaariset hahmot taistelevat maineesta, kunniasta ja mammonasta Frontierin laitamilla. Pelaa nyt ilmaiseksi Xbox Onella, PS4-järjestelmällä ja PC:llä Originin kautta.

localizations.de-DE.title: Apex Legends Fight or Fright-Event-Trailer
localizations.de-DE.description:
Vom 22. Oktober bis zum 3. November heißt es im Rahmen des Fight or Fright-Events Süßes oder Saures. Ein unheimlicher neuer Modus, gespenstische Herausforderungen und spektakuläre Belohnungen. Mehr erfahren.

Spiele den neuen befristeten Modus ""Schatten Royale"" auf Königsschlucht bei Nacht, wo der Tod nur der Anfang ist. Kehre als Schatten zurück, um deine Gegner heimzusuchen und deinem Squad zu helfen. Mit irrem Tempo, tödlichen Klauen und der Fähigkeit, deine Teammitglieder wiederzubeleben, bist du allen einen Schritt voraus. Und du kannst weitermachen, bis dein gesamter Squad ausradiert wurde. Nimm außerdem an unheimlichen Herausforderungen teil, um kostenlose Belohnungen zu erhalten und statte deine Legenden im Store mit neuen und klassischen kosmetischen Halloween-Objekten aus. Bist du bereit, die Arena zu terrorisieren?

Apex Legends™ ist ein Free-to-Play-Battle-Royale-Spiel, bei dem legendäre Charaktere am Rande des Grenzlands um Ruhm und Reichtum kämpfen. Jetzt kostenlos auf Xbox One, PS4 und Origin für PC spielen.

localizations.pl.title: Apex Legends – Walcz lub płacz: zwiastun wydarzenia
localizations.pl.description:
Cukierki poczekają, czas trochę napsocić – weź udział w wydarzeniu Walcz lub płacz w dniach 22 października – 3 listopada! Nowy, straszny tryb, upiorne wyzwania i niesamowite nagrody. Dowiedz się więcej.

Zagraj w nowy ograniczony czasowo tryb Cieniowe Royale na mapie Królewski Kanion w ciemności, gdzie śmierć jest dopiero początkiem. Jeśli zginiesz, odrodzisz się jako Cień, by nękać wrogów i wspierać swój oddział. Nic ci nie umknie – Cienie poruszają się diabelnie szybko, atakują śmiercionośnymi szponami i mogą reanimować swoich sojuszników. Jako Cień będziesz się odradzać, dopóki twój oddział nie zostanie wybity do nogi. Wykonuj przerażające wyzwania, by zdobyć obłędne darmowe nagrody i wyposażyć swoje legendy w klasyczne oraz całkiem nowe halloweenowe przedmioty kosmetyczne. Chcesz siać strach na arenie?

Apex Legends™ to darmowa gra Battle Royale, w której legendarne postacie mierzą się ze sobą w walce o sławę i chwałę na obrzeżach Kresów. Graj w Apex Legends za darmo już teraz – na Xbox One, PlayStation 4 oraz Origin na PC.

localizations.da.description:
Deltag i den skræmmende gode Fight or Fright-begivenhed fra den 22. oktober til den 3. november. Uhyggelig ny spiltype, skrækindjagende udfordringer og spektakulære belønninger. Få mere at vide

Prøv den nye ""Shadow Royale""-LTM i Kings Canyon After Dark, hvor døden kun er begyndelsen. Når du dør, bliver du gendannet som Shadow og kan jage dine fjender og hjælpe dit hold. Du kan bevæge dig med unaturlig fart, bruge dine dødbringende kløer og genopliv dine holdkammerater. Og du kan blive ved, indtil hele dit hold er blevet udslettet. Du kan også gennemføre skrækindjagende udfordringer for at få grumme, gratis belønninger og kostumer til dine legender med nye og klassiske halloween-kostumer i butikken. Er du klar til at sprede skræk i arenaen?

localizations.es-MX.description:
¡Atrévete a entrar en el evento Lucha o pesadilla del 22 de octubre al 3 de noviembre! Un nuevo modo aterrador, desafíos espeluznantes y recompensas espectaculares. Más información

Juega el nuevo modo por tiempo limitado Shadow Royale en Cañón de los Reyes al anochecer, donde la muerte solo es el comienzo. Reaparece como una sombra para acechar a tus enemigos y ayudar a tu escuadrón. Con una velocidad aterradora, garras letales y la habilidad de reanimar a tus compañeros, tendrás todo a tu favor. Y podrás seguir hasta que todo tu escuadrón quede eliminado. Además, completa desafíos espeluznantes para ganar recompensas gratuitas y elementos cosméticos nuevos y clásicos de Halloween para tus leyendas en la Tienda. ¿Te apetece aterrorizar la arena?

snippet.title: Hummer EV First Look! All The Details Of GMC's All-Electric Supertruck
snippet.description:
2022 GMC Hummer EV Is The World's First All-Electric Supertruck
Crab Mode, Watts To Freedom, e4WD, Extract Mode, and all the details!
Subscribe for new videos every Wednesday! - https://goo.gl/VZstk7
Recommended Books & Car Products - http://amzn.to/2BrekJm

The 2022 GMC Hummer EV's goal is to be "the most capable factory truck - ever,” said Al Oppenheiser, chief engineer. The Hummer EV has 1,000 HP, 11,500 lb-ft of wheel torque, three 250 kW electric motors, and a battery pack good for 350+ miles of range. 

GMC's Supertruck is packed with features: 4-Wheel steering featuring Crab Mode, Extract Mode, an Adaptive Air Suspension, 35-inch Goodyear Wrangler Tires, Underbody armor, UltraVision camera system, 24-module double-stacked Ultium battery propulsion system, three-motor e4WD system, Super Cruise, Watts to Freedom Mode, Driver Modes, Adaptive Ride Control, Open-air driving, Animal-free interior, 13.4" Infotainment display, MultiPro Tailgate, and a power-drop rear window. Check out the video to learn all the details of the 2022 GMC Hummer EV!

Engineering Explained is a participant in the Amazon Influencer Program.

snippet.title: The Sims 4 Snowy Escape: Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Experience the chilly thrills of mountain life in The Sims™ 4 Snowy Escape Expansion Pack!* Start planning your escape with snow sports, hot springs, and more now: http://x.ea.com/65833.

Find out what it means to touch the sky and reach a zen state of mind in Mt. Komorebi. Jump into the excitement of skiing, snowboarding, sledding, and rock climbing with new adventures for your Sims, or simply relax on slow hikes or at the onsen. See you there! 

Available November 13, 2020, on PC/Mac, Steam, Xbox One, and PlayStation®4.

Learn more about this Expansion Pack: http://x.ea.com/65833. 
Preorder now: http://x.ea.com/65834. 

#TheSims4 #Sims4SnowyEscape #SnowyEscape #Sims4

*REQUIRES THE SIMS 4 (SOLD SEPARATELY) AND ALL GAME UPDATES. FOR PC, SEE MINIMUM SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS FOR THE PACK.

localizations.ja.title: 「The Sims 4 Snowy Escape」: 公式発表トレーラー
localizations.ja.description:
「The Sims™ 4 Snowy Escape Expansion Pack」（※）で冬山を舞台にワクワクする体験を楽しもう！ スノースポーツに温泉、その他いろいろが待っている: http://x.ea.com/65833.

コモレビ山で空の高みに触れて、心落ち着く新たな境地に到達。スキー、スノーボード、ソリ、ロッククライミングで爽快なスリルを味わったり、ゆったりとしたハイキングや温泉で心や体を休めたり。さあ皆さんの訪れを待っています！

PC/Mac、Steam、Xbox One、PlayStation®4で2020年11月13日発売。

この拡張パックの詳細はこちら: http://x.ea.com/65833.
いますぐ予約: http://x.ea.com/65834.

（※）プレイには「The Sims 4」ゲーム本編（別売）と、すべてのゲームアップデートの適用が必要です。PC版は本パックの必要動作環境をご確認ください。
localizations.es-ES.title: Los Sims 4 Escapada en la Nieve: tráiler de presentación oficial
localizations.es-ES.description:
¡Disfruta las emociones de la vida en la montaña en Los Sims™ 4 Escapada en la Nieve Pack de Expansión!* Empieza ya a planear tu escapada con deportes de invierno, aguas termales y mucho más: http://x.ea.com/65833.

Descubre lo que significa tocar el cielo y alcanzar un estado mental zen en el monte Komorebi. Siente la emoción de esquiar, hacer snowboard, montar en trineo y escalar con nuevas aventuras o relájate haciendo excursiones más tranquilas o en el onsen. ¡Nos vemos allí! 

Disponible el 13 de noviembre de 2020 para PC/Mac, Steam, Xbox One y PlayStation®4.

Descubre más cosas sobre este pack de expansión: http://x.ea.com/65833. 
Resérvalo ya: http://x.ea.com/65834. 

*SE NECESITA LOS SIMS 4 (SE VENDE POR SEPARADO) CON TODAS SUS ACTUALIZACIONES. CONSULTA LOS REQUISITOS MÍNIMOS DEL SISTEMA DEL PACK PARA PC.

Viva as emoções geladas da vida na montanha em The Sims™ 4 Pacote de Expansão Diversão na Neve!* Comece a planejar agora a sua escapada com esportes na neve, fontes termais e muito mais: http://x.ea.com/65833.

Descubra como é tocar o céu e alcançar um estado mental zen no Monte Komorebi. Sinta a adrenalina praticando esqui e snowboarding, andando de trenó e fazendo escaladas com novas aventuras para os seus Sims, ou apenas relaxe em caminhadas tranquilas ou no onsen. Até lá!

Descobre mais sobre este Expansion Pack: http://x.ea.com/65833. 
Reserva já: http://x.ea.com/65834. 

*REQUER THE SIMS 4 (VENDIDO EM SEPARADO) E DE TODAS AS ATUALIZAÇÕES. PARA PC, CONSULTA OS REQUISITOS MÍNIMOS DE SISTEMA PARA ESTE PACK.
localizations.ko.title: The Sims 4 겨울이야기: 공식 발표 트레일러
localizations.ko.description:
The Sims™ 4 겨울이야기 확장팩*에서 설원의 산이 선사하는 스릴 넘치는 즐거움을 체험하세요! 설원 스포츠, 온천 등이 기다리는 휴양지로 떠나보세요! http://x.ea.com/65833

코모레비산에서 하늘을 만지면 어떤 기분인지, 평온한 기분에 드는 것이 무엇인지 알아보세요. 짜릿한 스키, 스노보드, 눈썰매, 암벽 등반에 도전하세요. 새로운 모험을 즐기거나 편안하게 온천에서 휴식하거나 한가로운 산행도 좋습니다. 그럼 곧 만나요! 

2020년 11월 13일 PC/Mac, Steam, Xbox One, PlayStation®4용으로 출시됩니다.

이 확장팩에 관해 자세히 알아보기: http://x.ea.com/65833. 
지금 예약 구매: http://x.ea.com/65834. 

*플레이하려면 THE SIMS 4 게임 (별매) 및 모든 게임 업데이트가 필요합니다. 이 팩의 PC 최소 사양을 확인하세요.
localizations.no.title: The Sims 4 Snøparadis: Avsløringstrailer
localizations.no.description:
Opplev den kalde spenningen på fjellet i The Sims™ 4 Snøparadis Utvidelsespakke!* Start planleggingen av utflukten med vintersport, varme kilder og mer nå: http://x.ea.com/65833 

Finn ut hva det betyr å nå både himmelen og en zen-tilstand på Komorebifjellet. Hopp inn i en spennende verden på slalåm, snowboard, aking og fjellklatring med nye eventyr for simmene, eller bare slapp av på rolige fotturer eller ved Onsen. Vi sees! 

Ute 13. november 2020 på PC/Mac, Steam, Xbox One og PlayStation®4.

Les mer om denne utvidelsespakken: http://x.ea.com/65833
Forhåndsbestill nå: http://x.ea.com/65834 

*KREVER AT DU HAR THE SIMS 4-GRUNNSPILLET (SELGES SEPARAT) OG ALLE SPILLOPPDATERINGENE. FOR PC: SJEKK MINSTE SYSTEMKRAV FOR DENNE PAKKEN.
localizations.fr-FR.title: Les Sims 4 Escapade enneigée : bande-annonce officielle de révélation
localizations.fr-FR.description:
Vivez les sensations fortes et froides de la vie à la montagne dans le pack d'extension Les Sims™ 4 Escapade enneigée !* Commencez dès maintenant à organiser votre escapade avec des sports d'hiver, des sources chaudes et bien plus encore : http://x.ea.com/65833.

Découvrez ce que signifie atteindre le sommet et devenir totalement zen à Mont Komorebi. Lancez-vous dans des activités palpitantes comme le ski, le snowboard, la luge et l'escalade avec des aventures inédites pour vos Sims, ou détendez-vous simplement en faisant des randonnées à votre rythme ou en allant à l'onsen. On se voit là-bas ! 

Disponible le 13 novembre 2020 sur PC/Mac, Steam, Xbox One et PlayStation®4.

Plus d'informations sur ce pack d'extension : http://x.ea.com/65833. 
Précommandez dès maintenant : http://x.ea.com/65834. 

*NÉCESSITE LE JEU LES SIMS 4 (VENDU SÉPARÉMENT) ET TOUTES SES MISES À JOUR. SI VOUS JOUEZ SUR PC, CONSULTEZ LA CONFIGURATION MINIMALE REQUISE POUR CE PACK.
localizations.sv.title: The Sims 4 Snöiga bergen: Officiell presentationstrailer
localizations.sv.description:
Upplev den iskalla spänningen bland bergen i The Sims™ 4 Snöiga bergen Expansion Pack!* Börja planera din vardagsflykt med snösporter, varma källor och mer, redan nu: http://x.ea.com/65833.

Ta reda på vad det innebär att ha huvudet bland molnen och att få sinnet att nå ett tillstånd av zen, i Mt. Komorebi. Kasta dig ut i spännande backar på skidor, snowboard och släde, ge dina simmar nya bergsklättringsäventyr eller ta det bara lugnt på en fotvandring eller i ett onsenbad. Vi ses där! 

Släpps 13 november 2020 till PC/Mac, Steam, Xbox One och PlayStation®4.

Läs mer om detta Expansion Pack: http://x.ea.com/65833. 
Förboka nu: http://x.ea.com/65834. 

*KRÄVER THE SIMS 4 (SÄLJS SEPARAT) OCH ALLA SPELUPPDATERINGAR. FÖR PC, SE MINIMISYSTEMKRAVEN FÖR DETTA PACK.
localizations.it.title: The Sims 4 Oasi Innevata: trailer della presentazione ufficiale
localizations.it.description:
Vivi emozioni da brivido in montagna con The Sims™ 4 Oasi Innevata Expansion Pack!* Inizia subito a pensare alla tua vacanza all'insegna di sport invernali, sorgenti termali e molto altro: http://x.ea.com/65833

Scopri cosa significa toccare il cielo e raggiungere uno stato mentale zen sul monte Komorebi. Tuffati nel divertimento con gli sci, lo snowboard, la slitta e le arrampicate affrontando le nuove avventure dei tuoi Sims, oppure rilassati facendo escursioni o all'Onsen. Ci vediamo lì! 

Disponibile il 13 novembre 2020 per PC/Mac, Steam, Xbox One e PlayStation®4.

Scopri i dettagli dell'Expansion Pack: http://x.ea.com/65833 
Prenota subito: http://x.ea.com/65834

*RICHIEDE THE SIMS 4 (VENDUTO SEPARATAMENTE) E TUTTI GLI AGGIORNAMENTI DEL GIOCO. PER PC, LEGGI I REQUISITI MINIMI DI SISTEMA DEL PACCHETTO.
localizations.nl-NL.title: Officiële onthullingstrailer van De Sims 4 Sneeuwpret
localizations.nl-NL.description:
Ervaar de ijskoude pret van het bergleven in het De Sims™ 4 Sneeuwpret Expansion Pack!* Boek nu je ultieme ontsnapping met sneeuwsport, warmwaterbronnen en meer: http://x.ea.com/65833.

Ontdek wat het betekent om de lucht aan te kunnen raken en compleet zen te worden in Mt. Komorebi. Beoefen spannende sneeuwsporten als skiën, snowboarden, sleeën en bergbeklimmen met tal van nieuwe avonturen voor je Sims. Of doe het juist rustig aan en relax met ontspannen wandelingen of een sessie in het Onsen Badhuis. Zie je daar! 

Verkrijgbaar vanaf 13 november 2020 op pc, Mac, Steam, Xbox One en PlayStation®4.

Kom meer te weten over dit Expansion Pack: http://x.ea.com/65833. 
Pre-order nu: http://x.ea.com/65834. 

*OM TE SPELEN HEB JE DE GAME DE SIMS 4 (LOS VERKRIJGBAAR) EN ALLE UPDATES NODIG. VOOR PC ZIE MINIMALE SYSTEEMVEREISTEN VOOR DIT PACK.
localizations.ru.title: Официальный трейлер игрового процесса «The Sims 4 Снежные просторы»
localizations.ru.description:
Получите острые ощущения от жизни в горах в «The Sims™ 4 Снежные просторы Дополнение»!* Устройте отдых с зимними видами спорта и горячими источниками и получите новые впечатления: http://x.ea.com/65833.

Узнайте, каково это дотянуться до небес или обрести душевное равновесие, посетив гору Комореби. Катайтесь на лыжах, сноуборде и санках, совершайте восхождения, просто гуляйте и дышите горным воздухом или расслабляйтесь в бане онсэн. До встречи на снежных просторах! 

С 13 ноября 2020 года на ПК/Mac, Steam, Xbox One и PlayStation®4.

Подробнее про дополнение: http://x.ea.com/65833. 
Оформить предазказ: http://x.ea.com/65834. 

* ДЛЯ ИГРЫ ТРЕБУЕТСЯ НАЛИЧИЕ THE SIMS 4 (ПРОДАЕТСЯ ОТДЕЛЬНО) И ВСЕХ ОБНОВЛЕНИЙ. СМ. МИНИМАЛЬНЫЕ СИСТЕМНЫЕ ТРЕБОВАНИЯ ДЛЯ НАБОРА НА ПК.
localizations.fi.title: The Sims 4 Lumisten vuorten maa: virallinen paljastustraileri
localizations.fi.description:
Koe vuoristoelämän riemut The Sims™ 4 Lumisten vuorten maa Expansion Packissä!* Suunnittele simeillesi pako arjesta talviurheilun, kuumien lähteiden ja muun mukavan parissa: http://x.ea.com/65833.

Komorebi-vuorella simeillesi selviää, miltä tuntuu koskettaa taivasta ja saavuttaa sisäinen rauha. Vie simisi nauttimaan laskettelun, lumilautailun, pulkkailun tai vuorikiipeilyn jännityksestä tai rentoutumaan patikkaretkelle tai onseniin. Nähdään siellä! 

Saatavilla 13. marraskuuta 2020 PC:llä/Macillä, Steam-palvelussa, Xbox Onella ja PlayStation®4-järjestelmällä.

Lue lisää tästä Expansion Packistä: http://x.ea.com/65833. 
Ennakkotilaa nyt: http://x.ea.com/65834. 

*PELAAMISEEN TARVITAAN THE SIMS 4 -PELI (MYYDÄÄN ERIKSEEN) JA KAIKKI PELIPÄIVITYKSET. LUE PAKETIN PC-JÄRJESTELMÄVAATIMUKSET.
localizations.de-DE.title: Die Sims 4 Ab ins Schneeparadies: Offizieller Enthüllungstrailer
localizations.de-DE.description:
Genieße eine spannende Zeit im Gebirge mit dem Die Sims™ 4 Ab ins Schneeparadies-Erweiterungspack!* Plane einen Urlaub mit Snowboarden, heißen Quellen und mehr: http://x.ea.com/65833.

Finde in Mt. Komorebi heraus, was es bedeutet, den Himmel zu berühren und den Zen-Zustand zu erreichen. Stürze dich beim Skifahren, Snowboarden, Schlittenfahren und Bergsteigen in neue Abenteuer oder entspanne dich bei einem ruhigen Spaziergang und im Badehaus. Wir sehen uns in Mt. Komorebi! 

Ab 13. November 2020 für PC/Mac, Steam, Xbox One und PlayStation®4 erhältlich.

Erfahre mehr über dieses Erweiterungspack: http://x.ea.com/65833. 
Jetzt vorbestellen: http://x.ea.com/65834. 

*BENÖTIGT DIE SIMS 4 (SEPARATER VERKAUF) UND ALLE SPIELUPDATES. SIEH DIR DIE PC-MINDESTANFORDERUNGEN FÜR DIESES PACK AN.
localizations.pl.title: The Sims 4 Śnieżna eskapada: oficjalny zwiastun
localizations.pl.description:
Doświadcz mroźnych, górskich wrażeń w The Sims™ 4 Śnieżna eskapada Dodatek!* Już teraz zaplanuj swoją eskapadę, pełną sportów zimowych, gorących źródeł i nie tylko: http://x.ea.com/65833.

Przekonaj się, jak to jest sięgnąć nieba i osiągnąć stan zen na górze Komorebi. Wskocz do ekscytującego świata nart, snowboardu, sanek i wspinaczki – zapewnij swoim Simom nowe przygody lub pozwól im odprężyć się w onsenie albo podczas niespiesznych wędrówek. Do zobaczenia! 

13 listopada 2020 r. premiera wersji na komputery PC/Mac, Steam oraz Xbox One i PlayStation®4.

Więcej informacji na temat tego Dodatku na stronie: http://x.ea.com/65833. 
Zamów w przedsprzedaży: http://x.ea.com/65834. 

*WYMAGA GRY THE SIMS 4 (SPRZEDAWANEJ ODDZIELNIE) I WSZYSTKICH JEJ AKTUALIZACJI. SPRAWDŹ MINIMALNE WYMAGANIA SYSTEMOWE TEGO PAKIETU W WERSJI NA PC.
localizations.da.title: The Sims 4 Snedrømme: officiel afsløringstrailer
localizations.da.description:
Se de spændende aktiviteter, du kan more dig med på de sneklædte bjerge i The Sims™ 4 Snedrømme Expansion Pack!* Udlev dine snedrømme nu med vintersport, varme kilder og meget mere: http://x.ea.com/65833.

Bestig Komorebi-bjerget, og opnå zen på verdens top. Din simmer kan se frem til nye eventyr: Prøv kræfter med at stå på ski og snowboard, tag en kælketur, eller bestig et bjerg! Du kan også bare tage en rolig vandretur eller slappe af i onsen. Vi ses derude! 

Udkommer d. 13. september 2020 til pc/Mac, Steam, Xbox One og PlayStation®4.

Få mere at vide om denne Expansion Pack: http://x.ea.com/65833. 
Forudbestil nu: http://x.ea.com/65834. 

*KRÆVER THE SIMS 4 (SÆLGES SEPARAT) SAMT ALLE SPILOPDATERINGER. SE MINIMUMSKRAV FOR DENNE PAKKE TIL PC.
localizations.es-MX.title: Los Sims 4 Escapada en la Nieve: tráiler de anuncio oficial
localizations.es-MX.description:
¡Disfruta las emociones de la vida en la montaña con Los Sims™ 4 Escapada en la Nieve Pack de Expansión!* Comienza a planear tu escapada con deportes de nieve, aguas termales y más ahora: http://x.ea.com/65833.

Descubre qué se siente al tocar el cielo y alcanzar el estado zen en el monte Komorebi. Pásala bien practicando esquí, snow, andando en trineo y haciendo escalada con las nuevas aventuras para tus Sims o simplemente relájate haciendo pequeñas caminatas o en el onsen. ¡Nos vemos allá! 

Disponible el 13 de noviembre de 2020 en PC/Mac, Steam, Xbox One y PlayStation®4.

Descubre más sobre este Pack de Expansión: http://x.ea.com/65833. 
Resérvalo ahora: http://x.ea.com/65834. 

*SE REQUIERE LOS SIMS 4 (SE VENDE POR SEPARADO) Y TODAS LAS ACTUALIZACIONES DEL JUEGO. CONSULTA LOS REQUISITOS MÍNIMOS DEL SISTEMA PARA EL PACK EN PC.
localizations.zh-CN.title: 《The Sims 4 雪境仙踪》：官方发布预告片
localizations.zh-CN.description:
在《The Sims™ 4 雪境仙踪》资料片中，体验寒冷刺激的山上生活！ * 现在开始用雪上运动、温泉、及更多活动，来计划你的遁世之旅：http://x.ea.com/65833。

在树影斑驳山中体会触摸天际、找寻内心禅意的感受。让模拟市民投身全新冒险，体验滑雪、单板滑雪、滑雪橇以及攀岩的精彩乐趣，还可以去徒步慢行或泡温泉。到时候见啦！

将于 2020 年 11 月 13 日登陆 PC/Mac、Steam、Xbox One 和PlayStation®4。

了解更多有关此资料片的信息，请访问：http://x.ea.com/65833。
立即预购：http://x.ea.com/65834。

*需搭配《The Sims 4》（另售）并安装所有游戏更新。 PC平台请参阅此资料片的最低系统要求。
localizations.cs.title: The Sims 4 Život na horách: Oficiální upoutávka s oznámením
localizations.cs.description:
Vychutnávejte ledový adrenalin horského života v rozšíření The Sims™ 4 Život na horách!* Naplánujte si svůj nový život plný zimních sportů, horkých pramenů a všeho dalšího: http://x.ea.com/65833.

Objevte, jaký je to pocit dostat se úplně na vrchol a dosáhnout emocionální rovnováhy na hoře Komorebi. Vrhněte se do zábavného lyžování, snowboardingu, sáňkování i horolezectví a dopřejte svým Simíkům nová dobrodružství nebo si prostě jen užívejte pohodu na pozvolných svazích nebo v onsenu. Uvidíme se tam! 

K dostání od 13. listopadu 2020 na PC/Mac, Steam, Xbox One a PlayStation®4.

Více informací o tomto rozšíření naleznete zde: http://x.ea.com/65833. 
Předobjednejte si: http://x.ea.com/65834. 

* VYŽADUJE ZÁKLADNÍ HRU THE SIMS 4 (V PRODEJI SAMOSTATNĚ) A VŠECHNY HERNÍ AKTUALIZACE. PROHLÉDNĚTE SI MINIMÁLNÍ SYSTÉMOVÉ POŽADAVKY TOHOTO BALÍČKU NA PC.
localizations.zh-TW.title: 《模擬市民 4 雪國勝地》：官方揭露預告片
localizations.zh-TW.description:
在《模擬市民™ 4 雪國勝地》資料片中，體驗寒冷刺激的登山生活！* 現在開始用雪上運動、溫泉、及其他活動，來規劃你的遁世之旅：http://x.ea.com/65833。

在木漏隙光山上體會觸摸天際、找尋內心禪意的感受。讓模擬市民投身新的冒險，體驗滑雪、單板滑雪、雪橇和攀岩的刺激樂趣，還可以去健行漫步或泡溫泉。到時候見！

於 2020 年 11 月 13 日 在 PC/Mac、Steam、Xbox One、和 PlayStation®4 上推出。

更多詳情請前往：http://x.ea.com/65833。
立即預購：http://x.ea.com/65834。

*需有《模擬市民 4》主遊戲（另售）與所有遊戲更新。PC 版請參閱此資料片的最低系統需求。

--- 
'McCartney III' - the new album, out December 11th 🎲
Pre-order: https://PaulMcCartney.lnk.to/McCartney3
 
50 years following the release of his self-titled first solo album McCartney, featuring Paul playing every instrument and writing and recording every song, Paul McCartney will release McCartney III on December 11th. Paul hadn’t planned to release an album in 2020, but in the isolation of “Rockdown,” he soon found himself fleshing out some existing musical sketches and creating even more new ones.

snippet.title: Raya and the Last Dragon | Official Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Restore peace. Find the last dragon. Watch the new trailer for Raya and the Last Dragon, in theaters March 2021.

Long ago, in the fantasy world of Kumandra, humans and dragons lived together in harmony. But when an evil force threatened the land, the dragons sacrificed themselves to save humanity. Now, 500 years later, that same evil has returned and it’s up to a lone warrior, Raya, to track down the legendary last dragon to restore the fractured land and its divided people. However, along her journey, she’ll learn that it’ll take more than a dragon to save the world—it’s going to take trust and teamwork as well. From directors Don Hall and Carlos López Estrada, co-directors Paul Briggs and John Ripa, producers Osnat Shurer and Peter Del Vecho, and featuring the voices of Kelly Marie Tran as Raya and Awkwafina as the last dragon Sisu, Walt Disney Animation Studios’ “Raya and the Last Dragon” opens in U.S. theaters on March 2021.

Facebook:  https://www.facebook.com/rayaandthelastdragon
Twitter:  https://twitter.com/DisneyRaya
Instagram:  https://www.instagram.com/disneyraya/
Hashtag: #DisneyRaya

snippet.title: Fortnitemares 2020 Midas' Revenge Gameplay Trailer - Fortnite
snippet.description:
Vengeance is a dish best... served... GOLD! Read more here: https://www.epicgames.com/fortnite/news/join-shadow-midas-to-get-revenge-in-fortnitemares-2020

Fortnitemares is back! From October 21 until November 3, rise to the occasion in the return of Fortnitemares. In Fortnitemares 2020: Midas’ Revenge, don’t let the tomb hold you back from haunting the living. And while you’re at it, live up your afterlife by vanquishing Challenges, catching a party, touring the Ghoulish Isles, and even cosplaying IRL.

Shadow Midas has taken over The Authority with his reawakened Henchmen. Stop him before you turn into a Shadow yourself. After being eliminated in Solo, Duos, or Squads, return to battle as a Shadow for your shot at a Shadow Royale. Join fellow Shadows to defeat survivors by using your otherworldly abilities, like possessing the body of vehicles…

Over the course of Fortnitemares, complete new Challenges to unlock special in-game rewards, including the Midas’ Shadow Wrap, Smash O’-Lantern Pickaxe, Bobo Back Bling, and more! Be seasonally-appropriate or stay scary year-round.

Also, Reggaeton Global ambassador superstar and four-time Latin GRAMMYⓇ winner J Balvin comes to Party Royale with the Afterlife Party, a special performance of Latin culture and hip-hop including the debut of his brand new song ft. Sech! The party begins at the Main Stage in Party Royale on October 31 at 9 PM ET (6 PM PT). 

Jump into Fortnitemares now!

#Fortnitemares #FortnitemaresChallenges #Fortnite


Play Fortnite Battle Royale, the completely free 100-player PvP mode. One giant map, A Battle Bus, Last one standing wins. ESRB Rating: Teen with Violence.

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/fortnite/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/FortniteGame
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/FortniteGame/

Learn More: https://www.epicgames.com/fortnite/en-US/

FAQ's ❤c

Q: Where is your accent from?
A: I was born and raised to Toronto, Ontario, Canada but moved to Essex in England when I was 14 years old. Hence my mixed up accent.

Q: Do you work? What do you work as?

Q: What camera do you use to film?
A: I film my videos with the Canon G7X and a Canon EOS M50.

Q: What lighting do you use?
A: I use natural lighting 90% of the time and a softbox light during the winter / dark evenings.

Q: Where do you get music from? 
A: Epidemic Sound, Soundcloud and the Youtube Library.

A: Yes I have a planner, and some jewellery. https://emilynorris.stilnest.com

snippet.title: Ryan & Shane Get Even Drunker & Read More Ghost Stories • Too Many Spirits
snippet.description:
Thank you Surfshark! Get Surfshark VPN at https://Surfshark.deals/watcher and enter the promo code WATCHER for 83% off and 3 extra months for free!

Welcome to episode 3 of our new spooky show- Too Many Spirits! Join us as we read your submitted ghost stories and enjoy cocktails prepared by first-time bartender, Steven Lim. If you've got even spookier stories, leave them in the comments below!

Please drink responsibly, and wear a mask.
This video was filmed under professional supervision. Alcohol intake was monitored, and talent was transported safely. Filming was conducted under recommended COVID-safe guidelines. 

Support us at:
http://www.patreon.com/watcher
http://www.watcherstore.com

Slim Reaper
2 tsp matcha
2 tbsp hot water
3/4th cup oat milk
3 tbsp Nigori sake
2 tbsp simple syrup

In a tea bowl, whisk matcha with hot water for ~1 minute. I’ve found that optimal stirring motions include a figure 8 mixed in with some circular action. After that’s complete, stir in the simple syrup and then pour that over the oat milk. Finally, mix the latte with Nigori sake and pour the final drink into a cup of ice!

snippet.title: Paul McCartney - McCartney III (Official Album Trailer)
snippet.description:
https://www.PaulMcCartney.com
--- 
'McCartney III' - the new album, out December 11th 🎲
Pre-order: https://PaulMcCartney.lnk.to/McCartney3
 
50 years following the release of his self-titled first solo album McCartney, featuring Paul playing every instrument and writing and recording every song, Paul McCartney will release McCartney III on December 11th. Paul hadn’t planned to release an album in 2020, but in the isolation of “Rockdown,” he soon found himself fleshing out some existing musical sketches and creating even more new ones.

localizations.zh-Hant.title: BLACKPINK曝光她們對彼此的真實想法 ｜ 誰，我？【英文字幕】
localizations.zh-Hant.description: 經過四年來一起訓練以及一起住宿舍的時間，BLACKPINK證明了她們對彼此的生活習慣有著徹底的了解。Lisa的友善以及Rosé的適應能力讓她們成為最有潛力的時光旅行者。Jisoo以及Jennie也分享了一些个人秘诀，能帮助他们在海外购物时获得最优惠的价格。
localizations.zh-Hans.title: BLACKPINK曝光她們對彼此的真實想法 ｜ 誰，我？【英文字幕】
localizations.zh-Hans.description: 經過四年來一起訓練以及一起住宿舍的時間，BLACKPINK證明了她們對彼此的生活習慣有著徹底的了解。Lisa的友善以及Rosé的適應能力讓她們成為最有潛力的時光旅行者。Jisoo以及Jennie也分享了一些个人秘诀，能帮助他们在海外购物时获得最优惠的价格。
localizations.th.title: BLACKPINK บอกเราว่าพวกเธอคิดต่อกันอย่างไรกันแน่ | ใครกัน ฉันเหรอ? [ซับไทย]
localizations.th.description: ด้วยประสบการณ์การฝึกและอยู่ด้วยกันมานานกว่าสี่ปี BLACKPINK โชว์ความรู้ขั้นกว่าของนิสัยของสมาชิก ความเป็นมิตรของลิซ่าและการปรับตัวเก่งของโรเซ่ทำให้พวกเธอน่าจะเป็นนักท่องเวลาที่ดีที่สุด จีซูและเจนนี่ให้เคล็ดลับส่วนตัวยามที่ไปช้อปปิ้งต่างประเทศ
localizations.ja.title: BLACKPINKのメンバーがお互いの印象について話しかける| 誰、私？[日本語字幕付き]
localizations.ja.description: 4年間以上の同僚生活とトレーニングがあるから、BLACKPINKのメンバーがお互いの性格と習慣について話す。リサのフレンドリー性格とロゼの適応性はタイムトラベラーに1番相応しいこと。そしてジスとジェニーは海外ショッピングについてどうやってお得なお買い上げを出来る情報もシェアします。
localizations.id.title: BLACKPINK memberitahu anggapan mereka tentang satu sama lain | Siapa, Aku? [INDO SUB]
localizations.id.description: Setelah latihan dan hidup bersama lebih dari 4 tahun, BLACKPINK menunjukkan pengetahuan tingkat atas mereka tentang sifat dan kebiasaan satu sama lain. Kami jadi tahu kalau keramahan Lisa dan kemampuan beradaptasi Rosé membuat mereka calon penjelajah waktu terbaik, lalu Jisoo dan Jennie berbagi tips pribadi tentang cara dapat harga murah saat belanja di luar negeri.

snippet.title: Ryan Giggs: Axel Tuanzebe Has All The Attributes!
snippet.description:
Ryan Giggs, Manchester United legend talks to Webby & O’Neill in this exclusive interview about Axel Tuanzebe after his impressive performance in the 1-2 win over PSG in the Champions League! Marcus Rashford MBE scored the winner and has been doing impressive work off the pitch, Ryan Giggs give his opinion on that and new signings Edinson Cavani, Alex Telles, Donny van de Beek ahead of the Premier League game vs Chelsea at the weekend. We saw Dan James play well in a more central position vs Newcastle, we hear his international managers opinion on that. Let us know what you think about all the topics in the comments!

Subscribe to Webby & O’Neill for more videos: https://bit.ly/WebbyONeill

Ryan Giggs is the most decorated player in the history of English football, winning an unbelievable 13 league titles, 2 Champions Leagues, 4 FA Cups, 3 League Cups and plenty more during his incredible career at Manchester United. Ryan is our record appearance maker with an incredible 963 appearances for the club. Ryan Giggs is the manager of Wales, the country he played for 64 times as a player.

Always brilliant to have a chat with Ryan Giggs! Let us know what you think about all the topics in the comments below…

Webby & O’Neill have been there and seen it all as Manchester United fans from winning the European Cup to relegation in the 1970’s. They’ve travelled the world following Man United for over 90 years combined and bring all that experience to their videos. Discussing all things relevant to Man Utd and the Premier League, Webby & O’Neill’s channel is the best place on YouTube to talk about England’s greatest football club.

Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/webbyoneill
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/webbyoneill

03:42 Ryan Giggs on Donny van de Beek & Alex Telles

snippet.title: Watch Three Space Travelers Return Home from the International Space Station
snippet.description:
NASA astronaut Chris Cassidy and cosmonauts Anatoly Ivanishin and Ivan Vagner of Roscosmos will return to Earth from the International Space Station on Wed., Oct. 21, 2020. Tune in for deorbit burn and landing coverage as their Soyuz spacecraft descends to a parachute-assisted landing, set for 10:55 p.m. EDT southeast of the remote town of Dzhezkazgan, Kazakhstan. 




The three crew members will wrap up a 196-day mission spanning 3,136 orbits of Earth and 83 million miles. Cassidy is completing his third spaceflight for a total of 378 days in space, the fifth highest total among U.S. astronauts. Ivanishin is completing his third flight into space, totaling 476 days. This was Vagner’s first spaceflight. During their expedition, Cassidy, Ivanishin, and Vagner welcomed the arrival of NASA astronauts Robert Behnken and Douglas Hurley on NASA’s SpaceX Demo-2 mission, the first crewed flight of a commercial spacecraft and the first launch of humans from American soil to the space station since 2011.

localizations.ja.title: 「The Sims 4 Snowy Escape」: 公式発表トレーラー
localizations.ja.description:
「The Sims™ 4 Snowy Escape Expansion Pack」（※）で冬山を舞台にワクワクする体験を楽しもう！ スノースポーツに温泉、その他いろいろが待っている: http://x.ea.com/65833.

コモレビ山で空の高みに触れて、心落ち着く新たな境地に到達。スキー、スノーボード、ソリ、ロッククライミングで爽快なスリルを味わったり、ゆったりとしたハイキングや温泉で心や体を休めたり。さあ皆さんの訪れを待っています！

この拡張パックの詳細はこちら: http://x.ea.com/65833.

localizations.es-ES.description:
¡Disfruta las emociones de la vida en la montaña en Los Sims™ 4 Escapada en la Nieve Pack de Expansión!* Empieza ya a planear tu escapada con deportes de invierno, aguas termales y mucho más: http://x.ea.com/65833.

Disponible el 13 de noviembre de 2020 para PC/Mac, Steam, Xbox One y PlayStation®4.

Viva as emoções geladas da vida na montanha em The Sims™ 4 Pacote de Expansão Diversão na Neve!* Comece a planejar agora a sua escapada com esportes na neve, fontes termais e muito mais: http://x.ea.com/65833.

Vive as refrescantes emoções da vida na montanha em The Sims™ 4 Snowy Escape Expansion Pack!* Começa já a planear a tua escapada com desportos na neve, termas e mais: http://x.ea.com/65833.

localizations.ko.description:
The Sims™ 4 겨울이야기 확장팩*에서 설원의 산이 선사하는 스릴 넘치는 즐거움을 체험하세요! 설원 스포츠, 온천 등이 기다리는 휴양지로 떠나보세요! http://x.ea.com/65833

코모레비산에서 하늘을 만지면 어떤 기분인지, 평온한 기분에 드는 것이 무엇인지 알아보세요. 짜릿한 스키, 스노보드, 눈썰매, 암벽 등반에 도전하세요. 새로운 모험을 즐기거나 편안하게 온천에서 휴식하거나 한가로운 산행도 좋습니다. 그럼 곧 만나요! 

2020년 11월 13일 PC/Mac, Steam, Xbox One, PlayStation®4용으로 출시됩니다.

localizations.fr-FR.title: Les Sims 4 Escapade enneigée : bande-annonce officielle de révélation
localizations.fr-FR.description:
Vivez les sensations fortes et froides de la vie à la montagne dans le pack d'extension Les Sims™ 4 Escapade enneigée !* Commencez dès maintenant à organiser votre escapade avec des sports d'hiver, des sources chaudes et bien plus encore : http://x.ea.com/65833.

Découvrez ce que signifie atteindre le sommet et devenir totalement zen à Mont Komorebi. Lancez-vous dans des activités palpitantes comme le ski, le snowboard, la luge et l'escalade avec des aventures inédites pour vos Sims, ou détendez-vous simplement en faisant des randonnées à votre rythme ou en allant à l'onsen. On se voit là-bas ! 

Disponible le 13 novembre 2020 sur PC/Mac, Steam, Xbox One et PlayStation®4.

Plus d'informations sur ce pack d'extension : http://x.ea.com/65833. 
Précommandez dès maintenant : http://x.ea.com/65834.

localizations.sv.title: The Sims 4 Snöiga bergen: Officiell presentationstrailer
localizations.sv.description:
Upplev den iskalla spänningen bland bergen i The Sims™ 4 Snöiga bergen Expansion Pack!* Börja planera din vardagsflykt med snösporter, varma källor och mer, redan nu: http://x.ea.com/65833.

Ta reda på vad det innebär att ha huvudet bland molnen och att få sinnet att nå ett tillstånd av zen, i Mt. Komorebi. Kasta dig ut i spännande backar på skidor, snowboard och släde, ge dina simmar nya bergsklättringsäventyr eller ta det bara lugnt på en fotvandring eller i ett onsenbad. Vi ses där!

localizations.it.title: The Sims 4 Oasi Innevata: trailer della presentazione ufficiale
localizations.it.description:
Vivi emozioni da brivido in montagna con The Sims™ 4 Oasi Innevata Expansion Pack!* Inizia subito a pensare alla tua vacanza all'insegna di sport invernali, sorgenti termali e molto altro: http://x.ea.com/65833

Scopri cosa significa toccare il cielo e raggiungere uno stato mentale zen sul monte Komorebi. Tuffati nel divertimento con gli sci, lo snowboard, la slitta e le arrampicate affrontando le nuove avventure dei tuoi Sims, oppure rilassati facendo escursioni o all'Onsen. Ci vediamo lì!

localizations.nl-NL.description:
Ervaar de ijskoude pret van het bergleven in het De Sims™ 4 Sneeuwpret Expansion Pack!* Boek nu je ultieme ontsnapping met sneeuwsport, warmwaterbronnen en meer: http://x.ea.com/65833.

Ontdek wat het betekent om de lucht aan te kunnen raken en compleet zen te worden in Mt. Komorebi. Beoefen spannende sneeuwsporten als skiën, snowboarden, sleeën en bergbeklimmen met tal van nieuwe avonturen voor je Sims. Of doe het juist rustig aan en relax met ontspannen wandelingen of een sessie in het Onsen Badhuis. Zie je daar!

localizations.ru.title: Официальный трейлер игрового процесса «The Sims 4 Снежные просторы»
localizations.ru.description:
Получите острые ощущения от жизни в горах в «The Sims™ 4 Снежные просторы Дополнение»!* Устройте отдых с зимними видами спорта и горячими источниками и получите новые впечатления: http://x.ea.com/65833.

Узнайте, каково это дотянуться до небес или обрести душевное равновесие, посетив гору Комореби. Катайтесь на лыжах, сноуборде и санках, совершайте восхождения, просто гуляйте и дышите горным воздухом или расслабляйтесь в бане онсэн. До встречи на снежных просторах!

localizations.fi.title: The Sims 4 Lumisten vuorten maa: virallinen paljastustraileri

Koe vuoristoelämän riemut The Sims™ 4 Lumisten vuorten maa Expansion Packissä!* Suunnittele simeillesi pako arjesta talviurheilun, kuumien lähteiden ja muun mukavan parissa: http://x.ea.com/65833.

Komorebi-vuorella simeillesi selviää, miltä tuntuu koskettaa taivasta ja saavuttaa sisäinen rauha. Vie simisi nauttimaan laskettelun, lumilautailun, pulkkailun tai vuorikiipeilyn jännityksestä tai rentoutumaan patikkaretkelle tai onseniin. Nähdään siellä!

localizations.de-DE.description:
Genieße eine spannende Zeit im Gebirge mit dem Die Sims™ 4 Ab ins Schneeparadies-Erweiterungspack!* Plane einen Urlaub mit Snowboarden, heißen Quellen und mehr: http://x.ea.com/65833.

Finde in Mt. Komorebi heraus, was es bedeutet, den Himmel zu berühren und den Zen-Zustand zu erreichen. Stürze dich beim Skifahren, Snowboarden, Schlittenfahren und Bergsteigen in neue Abenteuer oder entspanne dich bei einem ruhigen Spaziergang und im Badehaus. Wir sehen uns in Mt. Komorebi!

localizations.pl.title: The Sims 4 Śnieżna eskapada: oficjalny zwiastun

Doświadcz mroźnych, górskich wrażeń w The Sims™ 4 Śnieżna eskapada Dodatek!* Już teraz zaplanuj swoją eskapadę, pełną sportów zimowych, gorących źródeł i nie tylko: http://x.ea.com/65833.

Przekonaj się, jak to jest sięgnąć nieba i osiągnąć stan zen na górze Komorebi. Wskocz do ekscytującego świata nart, snowboardu, sanek i wspinaczki – zapewnij swoim Simom nowe przygody lub pozwól im odprężyć się w onsenie albo podczas niespiesznych wędrówek. Do zobaczenia!

Vychutnávejte ledový adrenalin horského života v rozšíření The Sims™ 4 Život na horách!* Naplánujte si svůj nový život plný zimních sportů, horkých pramenů a všeho dalšího: http://x.ea.com/65833.

snippet.title: iPhone 12 & 12 Pro Unboxing + MagSafe Accessories
snippet.description:
Unboxing the new iPhone 12 in product red and the new iPhone 12 Pro in gold. Also taking a closer look at a few MagSafe accessories. All these iPhones finally 5G so I’m using them on #Verizon 5G Ultra Wideband now available in Raleigh! Find out more about Verizon Ultra Wide and 5G here: https://www.Verizon.com

Drop any questions in the comment to be answered in a future video.

Big thank you to Verizon for supporting the channel and sponsoring a portion of this video.  All thoughts and opinions expressed are that of my own.

snippet.title: SEVENTEEN (세븐틴) 'HOME;RUN' Official MV
snippet.description:
SEVENTEEN (세븐틴) 'HOME;RUN' Official MV

세븐틴의 이번 앨범 ‘; [Semicolon]’은 미니 7집 ‘헹가래’를 통해 이야기한 ‘청춘’을 향한 응원의 메시지를 다시금 공유하면서 한 발짝 더 나아가 쉼 없이 달리는 청춘에게 ‘잠깐 쉬어가며 청춘의 향연을 즐기자’라는 더욱 성숙한 긍정의 메시지를 전하는 앨범이다.

현 시대를 살아가며 고군분투 하고 있는 청춘들에게 잠시나마 ‘숨 고를 시간’, ‘함께 웃으며 즐길 수 있는 시간’을 문장을 잠시 끊었다가 이어서 설명을 계속할 때 쓰이는 문장 부호인 ‘Semicolon(세미콜론)’ 에 비유, 동시대 청춘으로 살아가는 “세븐틴” 그들의 공감을 전하는 메시지를 앨범에 가득 담아내어 청춘들을 어루만질 따뜻한 위로와 응원, 공감을 주는 희망의 외침을 전한다.

타이틀곡 ‘HOME;RUN’은 스윙 장르 기반의 레트로한 사운드가 돋보이는 곡으로 경쾌하고 타격감 넘치는 사운드로 ‘HOME RUN’이라는 표현이 지닌 짜릿함을 표현하였고, 무한한 성장을 지닌 청춘에게 힘찬 응원과 위로의 목소리를 선사한다.

SEVENTEEN’s new album ‘; [Semicolon]’ is an album where they share the encouraging message for the ‘youth’ like they did in their 7th mini album ‘Heng:garæ’ and also the positive message that ‘we should all take a break and enjoy the youth’ with the youth that are running towards their goals without any breaks.

‘Semicolon,’ which is a punctuation mark used when you pause a sentence and then resume again, is used as a metaphor to portray the ‘time to take a breath’ and ‘time to laugh and enjoy together.’ “SEVENTEEN,” as the youth who are living in the same time period as the other youth who are fighting alone and struggling through their lives, uses this metaphor to convey their hopeful and empathic message through the album to comfort and cheer for the youth.

The title song ‘HOME;RUN’ is a song based on swing genre where the retro-like sound stands out, and it portrays the excitement that the phrase ‘HOME RUN’ conveys with cheerful and rhythmical sound. It conveys powerful support and comfort to the youth with limitless potentials.

#SEVENTEEN #세븐틴
#Semicolon #세미콜론
#HOME_RUN

‘Semicolon,’ which is a punctuation mark used when you pause a sentence and then resume again, is used as a metaphor to portray the ‘time to take a breath’ and ‘time to laugh and enjoy together.’ “SEVENTEEN,” as the youth who are living in the same time period as the other youth who are fighting alone and struggling through their lives, uses this metaphor to convey their hopeful and empathic message through the album to comfort and cheer for the youth.

The title song ‘HOME;RUN’ is a song based on swing genre where the retro-like sound stands out, and it portrays the excitement that the phrase ‘HOME RUN’ conveys with cheerful and rhythmical sound. It conveys powerful support and comfort to the youth with limitless potentials.

#SEVENTEEN #세븐틴
#Semicolon #세미콜론
#HOME_RUN

snippet.title: 林俊傑 JJ Lin《倖存者 Drifter》Official Music Video
snippet.description:
JJ 林俊傑 第14張專輯《倖存者 • 如你》雙EP 
雙維度 EP 創造全新音樂視角 

數位收聽｜https://jjlin.lnk.to/JJDrifterLikeYouDoYC
實體購買｜https://jjlin.lnk.to/JJXIVFA

林俊傑 x 賴雅妍 x 修杰楷
張榮吉 執導x 余靜萍 掌鏡 
高規格團隊打造 城市中最暖的視覺感官

城市中承載著多少偉大的夢想、渺小的希望
世界上又有多少角落的失望、低頭的沮喪
倖存於世界、倖存於社會
但，是否倖存於自己的內心所愛？

人來人往忙碌的現代世界，“冷漠“成為了生活進步的產物，JJ跳脫以往掏空內心的訴說方式，套入每個人的故事去唱「你我他的故事」。同為如此忙碌的現代人，長遠的夢想、或眼前的目標，就像傳輸帶一般被推著走的生活，努力追求似乎是唯一的解答，試圖拋出“快樂的定義是什麼？“，希望在每個可能重整的狀態中，能夠啟發不斷重新定義人生跟社會。

JJ 以口述的語氣，就像是一個低語的自我訴說者，化為每一位低頭專注自己世界的過客，知名作詞人小寒，用堅毅且剛硬的語句映出每個人為了過想過的生活，就像是一場戰爭，但字裡行間透露著內心深處的脆弱與無力，每一個肯定句，都在為自己的生命打氣，而最終在曲末扣回生命主體“愛”，將歌曲的溫度在經歷曲勢的猛烈炙燒後，停留在一個剛好適合取暖的溫度。

MV由 張榮吉執導、余靜萍掌鏡，兩人對畫面的默契以及對故事的詮釋，故事看似不相干的兩個時空，但藉由男主角對生命的熱情與對環境的傾力，讓兩個時空串起了密不可分的關係，而JJ依然以客串的姿態出現在自己的MV裡面，並接續著【交換餘生】的概念，扮演著兩個時空的連接點。

#JJ林俊傑倖存者
#JJ林俊傑倖存者如你
#JJDrifter
#JJDrifterLikeYouDo
#JJXIV #JJDoubleEP

_
倖存者    詞：小寒  曲：林俊傑

冷掉的飯盒 台詞對半摺
渴 這時候算什麼
而 心涼如薄荷 脆弱如蛋殼 
則 消失在這一刻

背著夢的倖存者 經過現實的拉扯
可 贏得了拔河 理念還剩幾毫克 
背負傷的倖存者 爭奪著有限名額
可 留下的有幾個  

有苦澀 忐忑 坎坷 
等著有了起色  
我要傷悄悄地癒合 命運別招惹 
  
曾想出爾 反爾 奈何
我宣言還言猶在耳
得對自己比別人對我嚴格  

有苦澀 忐忑 坎坷 
忍著有了起色   
我是否賺取了資格 可以來到這
生還不為巧合 或聞名遐邇
只是為了得到愛的人 認可

背著夢的倖存者 經歷生活的牽扯
可 持續的拔河 眼神可還會灼熱
背負傷的倖存者 代價是感情全額
可 我如何做取捨 嗚

夢的光澤在溫和應和   
是燈蛾總認得月兒
人生來就會漂流向 發著光的誘餌
  
雖然偶爾 我偶爾 想為何 
但諾言還言猶在耳
想要閃爍就對自己更嚴格 

夢的光澤在溫和地應和   
燈蛾不由得分隔
我是否已賺取了資格 可以站在這
生還不為巧合 或能聞名遐邇
只是為了得到愛的人 認可
真的
_

snippet.localized.title: 林俊傑 JJ Lin《倖存者 Drifter》Official Music Video
snippet.localized.description:
JJ 林俊傑 第14張專輯《倖存者 • 如你》雙EP 
雙維度 EP 創造全新音樂視角 

數位收聽｜https://jjlin.lnk.to/JJDrifterLikeYouDoYC
實體購買｜https://jjlin.lnk.to/JJXIVFA

林俊傑 x 賴雅妍 x 修杰楷
張榮吉 執導x 余靜萍 掌鏡 
高規格團隊打造 城市中最暖的視覺感官

城市中承載著多少偉大的夢想、渺小的希望
世界上又有多少角落的失望、低頭的沮喪
倖存於世界、倖存於社會
但，是否倖存於自己的內心所愛？

人來人往忙碌的現代世界，“冷漠“成為了生活進步的產物，JJ跳脫以往掏空內心的訴說方式，套入每個人的故事去唱「你我他的故事」。同為如此忙碌的現代人，長遠的夢想、或眼前的目標，就像傳輸帶一般被推著走的生活，努力追求似乎是唯一的解答，試圖拋出“快樂的定義是什麼？“，希望在每個可能重整的狀態中，能夠啟發不斷重新定義人生跟社會。

JJ 以口述的語氣，就像是一個低語的自我訴說者，化為每一位低頭專注自己世界的過客，知名作詞人小寒，用堅毅且剛硬的語句映出每個人為了過想過的生活，就像是一場戰爭，但字裡行間透露著內心深處的脆弱與無力，每一個肯定句，都在為自己的生命打氣，而最終在曲末扣回生命主體“愛”，將歌曲的溫度在經歷曲勢的猛烈炙燒後，停留在一個剛好適合取暖的溫度。

MV由 張榮吉執導、余靜萍掌鏡，兩人對畫面的默契以及對故事的詮釋，故事看似不相干的兩個時空，但藉由男主角對生命的熱情與對環境的傾力，讓兩個時空串起了密不可分的關係，而JJ依然以客串的姿態出現在自己的MV裡面，並接續著【交換餘生】的概念，扮演著兩個時空的連接點。

#JJ林俊傑倖存者
#JJ林俊傑倖存者如你
#JJDrifter
#JJDrifterLikeYouDo
#JJXIV #JJDoubleEP

_
倖存者    詞：小寒  曲：林俊傑

冷掉的飯盒 台詞對半摺
渴 這時候算什麼
而 心涼如薄荷 脆弱如蛋殼 
則 消失在這一刻

背著夢的倖存者 經過現實的拉扯
可 贏得了拔河 理念還剩幾毫克 
背負傷的倖存者 爭奪著有限名額
可 留下的有幾個  

有苦澀 忐忑 坎坷 
等著有了起色  
我要傷悄悄地癒合 命運別招惹 
  
曾想出爾 反爾 奈何
我宣言還言猶在耳
得對自己比別人對我嚴格  

有苦澀 忐忑 坎坷 
忍著有了起色   
我是否賺取了資格 可以來到這
生還不為巧合 或聞名遐邇
只是為了得到愛的人 認可

背著夢的倖存者 經歷生活的牽扯
可 持續的拔河 眼神可還會灼熱
背負傷的倖存者 代價是感情全額
可 我如何做取捨 嗚

夢的光澤在溫和應和   
是燈蛾總認得月兒
人生來就會漂流向 發著光的誘餌
  
雖然偶爾 我偶爾 想為何 
但諾言還言猶在耳
想要閃爍就對自己更嚴格 

夢的光澤在溫和地應和   
燈蛾不由得分隔
我是否已賺取了資格 可以站在這
生還不為巧合 或能聞名遐邇
只是為了得到愛的人 認可
真的
_

snippet.title: BLACKPINK – ‘Lovesick Girls’ M/V
snippet.description:
BLACKPINK – ‘Lovesick Girls’

영원한 밤
창문 없는 방에 우릴 가둔 love
What can we say
매번 아파도 외치는 love

다치고 망가져도 나
뭘 믿고 버티는 거야
어차피 떠나면 상처투성인 채로 미워하게 될걸
끝장을 보기 전 끝낼 순 없어
이 아픔을 기다린 것처럼

아마 다 잠깐 일지도 몰라
우린 무얼 찾아서 헤매는 걸까

But I don’t care I’ll do it over and over
내 세상 속엔 너만 있으면 돼

We are the lovesick girls
네 멋대로 내 사랑을 끝낼순 없어
We are the lovesick girls
이 아픔 없인 난 아무 의미가 없어

But we were born to be alone
Yeah we were born to be alone
Yeah we were born to be alone 
But why we still looking for love

No love letters, no x and o’s
No love never, my exes know
No diamond rings, that set in stone
To the left, better left alone

Didn’t wanna be a princess, I’m priceless
A prince not even on my list
Love is a drug that I quit
No doctor could help when I’m lovesick

아마 다 잠깐 일지도 몰라
우린 무얼 찾아서 헤매는 걸까

불안한 내 눈빛 속에 널 담아
아프더라도 너만 있으면 돼

We are the lovesick girls
네 멋대로 내 사랑을 끝낼 순 없어
We are the lovesick girls
이 아픔 없인 난 아무 의미가 없어

But we were born to be alone
Yeah we were born to be alone
Yeah we were born to be alone 
But why we still looking for love

사랑은 slippin’ and fallin’
사랑은 killin’ your darlin’
아프다 아물면 또 찾아오는 이 겁 없는 떨림

들리지 않아 what you say
이 아픔이 난 행복해
나를 불쌍해 하는 네가 내 눈엔 더 불쌍해

We are the lovesick girls
네 멋대로 내 사랑을 끝낼 순 없어
We are the lovesick girls
이 아픔없인 난 아무 의미가 없어

Lovesick girls 
모두 결국 떠나가고
Lovesick girls
내 눈물이 무뎌져도
Lovesick girls
아프고 또 아파도
Lovesick girls
But we’re still looking for love

Available on @ https://smarturl.it/BLACKPINKTHEALBUM  
Official BLACKPINK Merchandise: http://smarturl.it/BLACKPINKShop/

http://www.blackpinkofficial.com/

http://www.instagram.com/BLACKPINKOFFICIAL

snippet.title: Trump Now Crashing In 2020 As Some Fans Bolt, Echoing Trump U. Debacle | MSNBC
snippet.description:
New 2020 polls from six key states show some Trump 2016 voters abandoning him -- imperiling his narrow coalition. MSNBC's Ari Melber reports on why both the loyalty and enmity among Trump fans is different than for other politicians; and Melber documents how Trump customers turned on his con in the "Trump University" case and explores the parallels to Trump's political standing today. (This interview is from MSNBC’s “The Beat with Ari Melber, a news show covering politics, law and culture airing nightly at 6pm ET on MSNBC. http://www.thebeatwithari.com). Aired on 10/19/2020.
» Subscribe to MSNBC: http://on.msnbc.com/SubscribeTomsnbc

About The Beat with Ari Melber: Former lawyer Ari Melber leads this show that provides in-depth analysis of the day's biggest news stories. ""The Beat"" features guest interviews in addition to reporting on stories from across the country. The stories that are covered span across the political spectrum. In addition to his law background, Melber is a former Senate staffer, giving him a unique perspective to share on the political happenings coming out of Washington, D.C.

snippet.title: Hear U Out 权听你说 EP 20 | Eleanor Lee Part 1 李凯馨 上集
snippet.description:
This may be Yifong’s most difficult interview in her career – her daughter. Eleanor’s acting career in China took off without a hitch, her skyrocketing popularity also gaining her many fans. What is her motivation for trying to carve a career overseas? Eleanor once had difficulties in learning, how was she able to attain top marks in her art school’s entrance exam? 访问女儿是怡凤主持有史以来的最大挑战。凯馨在中国影视圈发展如鱼得水，累积众多海内外粉丝，人气扶摇直上。她拼命往外闯证明自己的真正原因是什么？天生我才必有用，曾有学习障碍的她，又如何在艺考突破重围，拿下好名次？

localizations.ja.description: 4年間以上の同僚生活とトレーニングがあるから、BLACKPINKのメンバーがお互いの性格と習慣について話す。リサのフレンドリー性格とロゼの適応性はタイムトラベラーに1番相応しいこと。そしてジスとジェニーは海外ショッピングについてどうやってお得なお買い上げを出来る情報もシェアします。
localizations.id.title: BLACKPINK memberitahu anggapan mereka tentang satu sama lain | Siapa, Aku? [INDO SUB]
localizations.id.description: Setelah latihan dan hidup bersama lebih dari 4 tahun, BLACKPINK menunjukkan pengetahuan tingkat atas mereka tentang sifat dan kebiasaan satu sama lain. Kami jadi tahu kalau keramahan Lisa dan kemampuan beradaptasi Rosé membuat mereka calon penjelajah waktu terbaik, lalu Jisoo dan Jennie berbagi tips pribadi tentang cara dapat harga murah saat belanja di luar negeri.

snippet.title: Kapuso Mo, Jessica Soho: Sino ang tunay na kadugo ng lalaki sa Southern Leyte?
snippet.description:

snippet.description:

snippet.title: Apple iPhone 12 event in under 12 minutes
snippet.description:
Apple’s iPhone 12 event just wrapped and it revealed the iPhone 12, iPhone 12 mini, iPhone 12 Pro and iPhone 12 Pro Max. Apple’s newest smartphones have a new design with flat edges, and they all support 5G wireless networks. Apple also unveiled the HomePod mini, a smaller and more affordable model in its smart speaker lineup.

snippet.title: iPhone 12 Pro review: more shine
snippet.description:

snippet.title: Trump Now Crashing In 2020 As Some Fans Bolt, Echoing Trump U. Debacle | MSNBC
snippet.description:
New 2020 polls from six key states show some Trump 2016 voters abandoning him -- imperiling his narrow coalition. MSNBC's Ari Melber reports on why both the loyalty and enmity among Trump fans is different than for other politicians; and Melber documents how Trump customers turned on his con in the "Trump University" case and explores the parallels to Trump's political standing today. (This interview is from MSNBC’s “The Beat with Ari Melber, a news show covering politics, law and culture airing nightly at 6pm ET on MSNBC. http://www.thebeatwithari.com). Aired on 10/19/2020.
» Subscribe to MSNBC: http://on.msnbc.com/SubscribeTomsnbc

About The Beat with Ari Melber: Former lawyer Ari Melber leads this show that provides in-depth analysis of the day's biggest news stories. ""The Beat"" features guest interviews in addition to reporting on stories from across the country. The stories that are covered span across the political spectrum. In addition to his law background, Melber is a former Senate staffer, giving him a unique perspective to share on the political happenings coming out of Washington, D.C.

MSNBC delivers breaking news, in-depth analysis of politics headlines, as well as commentary and informed perspectives. Find video clips and segments from The Rachel Maddow Show, Morning Joe, Meet the Press Daily, The Beat with Ari Melber, Deadline: White House with Nicolle Wallace, Hardball, All In, Last Word, 11th Hour, and more.

snippet.title: PART 2 | TEKLA, IPINAGTANGGOL NG MGA KASAMAHAN NYA SA SHOWBIZ!
snippet.description:
PART 1: https://youtu.be/Q7Rbrb28P0U


PART 3: https://youtu.be/zjDr7a6vQY4


MAHALAGANG PAALALA:

Muli po naming pinapaalala na hanggang ngayon ay SARADO PA RIN PO ANG AMING ACTION CENTER sa TV5 Media Center, Reliance Street, Mandaluyong City.

Hindi pa rin po maaaring pumunta nang personal ang mga complainant para magreklamo kay Idol Raffy dahil sa ating kinahaharap na pandemya at mahigpit pa ring ipinapatupad ang mga safety measures upang maging ligtas ang lahat.

Gayunpaman, puwede ninyong i-PM ang inyong mga sumbong sa OFFICIAL Facebook page ni Idol na RAFFY TULFO IN ACTION na may mahigit 11M followers. Nakahanda pong tumugon sa inyo ang RTIA researchers.

Maraming salamat sa inyong pag-unawa at mag-ingat po tayong lahat!

snippet.title: WORLD'S FASTEST ONBOARD: SSC Tuatara hits crazy 331mph top speed! | Top Gear
snippet.description:
Top Gear can exclusively reveal that Shelby SuperCars (SSC) North America has set a new production car top speed record, hitting a VMAX of 331mph and setting a two-way average of 316.11mph on a seven-mile stretch of closed road just outside of Las Vegas, Nevada. Climb on board for the outrageous 0-331mph run as Top Gear is granted exclusive footage from the guys that are making the full feature-length documentary of this epic endeavour, landing later in the year. For the full story on this wild new world record and just how SSC stole Bugatti’s crown, head to https://www.topgear.com/car-news/supercars/sscs-tuatara-fastest-car-world-331mph-top-speed
